{"tid":1567384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抄橋国技）逾百名愛国人士爬上香港獅子山 揮動国旗高唱国歌","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:12:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0eb216f535e09a046ad48d8d367a33e120d67f7","tid":1567384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"來源：中國日報<br />\n<br />\n9月14日一早，逾百名身著紅色T恤的愛國人士爬上象徵香港精神的獅子山，在山頂上揮動起鮮艷的五星紅旗及香港區旗，高唱中華人民共和國國歌，和《歌唱祖國》，並高喊「祖國萬歲」、「我自豪，我是中國人」，慶祝#新中國成立七十周年#。響亮的聲音回蕩在山谷，這才是真正的獅子山精神！<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190914/32654568.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e05ea4df11124c36be53d4ba1df687139b080676","tid":1567384,"uid":121937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"no one care<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60866a44014eb25c72a783ebf4261345a57e9d2e","tid":1567384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"東方：30紅衣人獅子山展示五星旗區旗<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190914/mobile/bkn-20190914104713219-0914_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f962b61f3cebd61f9ec05775af7d2163bb40444e","tid":1567384,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faf6919bab8fc99d4737e04119dfc4236d69c5df","tid":1567384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60866a44014eb2